-- 2010-12-29T18:00:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-29/brett-favre-fined-50-000-by-nfl-for-lack-of-cooperation-in-texting-probe.html
Brett Favre was fined $50,000 by the
National Football League for a lack of cooperation in its
investigation of suggestive messages he allegedly sent to a
female co-worker when both were with the New York Jets in 2008.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  